snippet.title: Nonsense Soccer Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Nonsense Soccer is coming to Steam Early Access 16 October! Mark your calendars!

Check out this uniquely chaotic, local multiplayer platformer-soccer-hybrid from @AnttiKole.
